OL,3,CBoxer Joe Cordina accused of
OL,4,Cassaulting another man, court hears
OL,6,FFormer boxing world champion Joe
OL,7,FCordina is accused of assaulting
OL,8,Fanother man, a court has heard.
OL,10,FCordina, 34, a two-time IBF super-
OL,11,Ffeatherweight champion, was not
OL,12,Frequired to attend a brief hearing at
OL,13,FCardiff Magistrates' Court on
OL,14,FWednesday.
OL,16,FHe is charged with assault by beating
OL,17,Fand threatening a person with an
OL,18,Foffensive weapon in a public place.
