OL,3,CBoxer Joe Cordina accused of
OL,4,Cassaulting another man, court hears
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police previously said in
OL,7,Fa statement that the charges relate to
OL,8,Fan incident outside Pentwyn Service
OL,9,FStation in Cardiff on February 27 this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FJamie O'Brien, 32, from Pentwyn, has
OL,13,Falso been charged with assault in
OL,14,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, Jeanine Robinson,
OL,17,Fprosecuting, said the offences the two
OL,18,Fmen are charged with are alleged to be
OL,19,F"against each other".
