OL,3,CBoxer Joe Cordina accused of
OL,4,Cassaulting another man, court hears
OL,6,FThe hearing was adjourned until July
OL,7,F28, when O'Brien is also scheduled to
OL,8,Fappear in court.
OL,10,FDistrict Judge Charlotte Murphy said:
OL,11,F"That is adjourned to July 28 at this
OL,12,Fcourt.
OL,14,F"I will require Mr Cordina to attend
OL,15,Fon this date."
OL,17,FCordina, of Pontprennau, was
OL,18,Frepresented by Nadeem Majid.
