OL,3,CBoxer Joe Cordina accused of
OL,4,Cassaulting another man, court hears
OL,6,FIn a statement, South Wales Police
OL,7,Fsaid previously: "Two men have been
OL,8,Fcharged in connection with an incident
OL,9,Foutside Pentwyn Service Station,
OL,10,FPentwyn Road, Cardiff, on February 27,
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,F"Joseph Cordina, 34, from Pontprennau,
OL,14,Fhas been charged with assault and
OL,15,Fthreatening a person with an offensive
OL,16,Fweapon in a public place. He is due to
OL,17,Fappear at Cardiff Magistrates' Court
OL,18,Fon July 7.
