OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1783680590
OL,3,CBoxer Joe Cordina accused of
OL,4,Cassaulting another man, court hears
OL,6,F"Jamie O'Brien, 32, from Pentwyn, has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with assault and is due
OL,8,Fto appear at Cardiff Magistrates'
OL,9,FCourt on July 28."
OL,11,FCordina was due to fight for the WBO
OL,12,Flightweight title in the United States
OL,13,Fon July 4, however, his application
OL,14,Ffor a US visa was refused.
